annotationA: Nitrilase and fragile histidine triad fusion protein NitFhit; Cleaves A-5'-PPP-5'A to yield AMP and ADP
annotationB: Ribokinase; Catalyzes the phosphorylation of ribose at O-5 in a reaction requiring ATP and magnesium. The resulting D-ribose-5- phosphate can then be used either for sythesis of nucleotides, histidine, and tryptophan, or as a component of the pentose phosphate pathway
